snippet.title: Resident Advisor
snippet.description:
Established in 2001, Resident Advisor (RA) is an online music magazine and community platform that's dedicated to showcasing electronic music, artists and events across the globe. RA combines high-quality writing and film features with listings, directories and industry tools, creating an ecosystem of content and services for million each month. With an audience spanning music fans, club goers, DJs, producers, venue owners, promoters and record labels, RA plays an indispensable role in supporting the electronic music industry worldwide.  

In 2011, RA Films launched with Real Scenes: Bristol, and has since continued to present in-depth documentaries that explore electronic music scenes across the world, shining light on emerging talent and profiling some of the industry’s key artists.
